<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-eq.wikidot.com/local--files/awbw/bde2810e595ffcba81653160c99a2f0f.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="bde2810e595ffcba81653160c99a2f0f.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
